15- 3-1998 Peru         3-3 Ecuador         [5-4 pen]

Final 
15- 3-1998 Brazil       7-1 Argentina

Brazil qualified for the 1999 World Cup; Argentina to play off with Mexico,
the runners-up of the CONCACAF qualifying zone.


